{17} {~Sacred~[TAG_MODIFIER_SACRED]} // I think this is the vanilla Sacred bonus type (only used by the Consecrate spell)
{18} {~Insight~[TAG_MODIFIER_INSIGHT]}
{19} {~Concealment~[TAG_CONCEALMENT]}
